а, а матери, которую звали Mary Bartholomew, 14. Она вышла замуж за человека по имени William Carter 15 октября 1599 г. в местности степни, миддлесекс, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Она умерла в 1605 г. в местности вестминстир, Лондон, Англия, Великобритания в возрасте 25 лет и была похоронена в местности Лондон, миддлесекс, Англия."},"sm":{"1580–1605":"1580–1605","1574–1605":"1574–1605","1601–1625":"1601–1625","1577–Male":"1577–Ua Maliu","1566–1607":"1566–1607","1580":"1580","1601":"1601","1600":"1600","1566":"1566","1577":"1577","1587":"1587","1585":"1585","1574":"1574","15 OCT 1599":"15 Oketopa 1599","15 Oct 1599":"15 Oketopa 1599","1607":"1607","Bef 31 March 1601":"a'e le'I oo le 31 Mati 1601","1605":"1605","1625":"1625","Westminster, London, England":"Westminster, London, Egelani, United Kingdom","St Dunstans, London, England":"Saint Dunstan and All Saints Church, Stepney, London, Egelani, United Kingdom","Stepney, Middlesex, England":"Stepney, Middlesex, Egelani","Saint Mary Somerset with Saint Mary Mounthaw, London, Middlesex, England":"London, Middlesex, Egelani","Saint Dunstan,Stepney,London,England":"Stepney, London, Egelani, United Kingdom","Saint Benet Gracechurch, London, Middlesex, England":"London, Middlesex, Egelani"},"sk":{"1580–1605":"1580–1605","1574–1605":"1574–1605","1601–1625":"1601–1625","1577–Male":"1577–Zosnulý","1566–1607":"1566–1607","1580":"1580","1601":"1601","1600":"1600","1566":"1566","1577":"1577","1587":"1587","1585":"1585","1574":"1574","15 OCT 1599":"15. október 1599","15 Oct 1599":"15. október 1599","1607":"1607","Bef 31 March 1601":"pred rokom 31. marec 1601","1605":"1605","1625":"1625","Westminster, London, England":"Westminster, London, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","St Dunstans, London, England":"Saint Dunstan and All Saints Church, Stepney, London, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Stepney, Middlesex, England":"Stepney, Middlesex, England","Saint Mary Somerset with Saint Mary Mounthaw, London, Middlesex, England":"Lon